<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٢٦٣ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5360">مَالِكُ بْنُ إِسْمَاعِيلَ </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2110">زُهَيْرٌ </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6702">هِشَامٌ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4361">عُرْوَةَ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ </a><span class="special">﵂</span> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«الْحُمَّى مِنْ فَيْحِ جَهَنَّمَ فَأبْرُدُوهَا بِالْمَاءِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>